snippet.title: PowerWash Simulator | Ice Rink Winter Seasonal 2024
snippet.description:
Ho-Ho-Hold on to your PowerWashers, it's about to get chilly in Muckingham❄️

Step into Christmas with our new Winter Seasonal, The Ice Rink! 

Yule be able to unwrap this holiday gift right now for free now on PC, Xbox One, Xbox Series S|X, PlayStation 4|5 and Nintendo Switch ☃️

PowerWash Sim is available on PlayStation 5, PlayStation 4, Nintendo Switch, Xbox Series S|X, Xbox One, Windows, and Steam. Plus, it is included with Xbox Game Pass and PlayStation Plus! 

Play PowerWash Simulator on Steam here: https://steamcommunity.com/app/1290000  

 
For more pressure washing goodness, subscribe to our channel!  

Follow our Twitter for daily satisfying content: https://bit.ly/TwitterPWS  
Join our Discord to join the conversation: https://discord.gg/powerwashsimulator  
Follow us on TikTok for quick spray socials: https://bit.ly/PWSTikTok  

 
#PowerWashSimulator #Christmas #Gaming
